data.description: Beautiful treed .90 acre lot located in Athens City Limits. This full brick ranch home offers 3 bedrooms and 2 baths with office that could be a small bedroom. Living room has original hardwood floors with ceiling fan. Kitchen has stainless steel appliances, gas stove, microwave, dishwasher. Island separates kitchen from dining area. Family room with fireplace with wood burning stove insert, laminate floors, ceiling fan. Outside is a covered front porch with patio area, storage room, 2- detached storage buildings, 36x16 & 12x14 with electricity, covered back patio area, fenced in yard.
